<span class="header1">Technology paired with Public Service (FG)</span>

<p>You will be a valued member of the work force. You are very community minded and prefer a "hands-on" approach. You want to make the world a better place through technology.  There are many occupations that require being able to work with people, machines, and tools.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree. It is helpful to have a Master's Degree or Ph.D. if you hope to work in some of these occupations.</p>

